<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔的妻子对食人魔摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是那个男孩儿。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你闻到的可能是昨天的晚饭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔生气地走了几步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“忘了他吧。”妻子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我给你做一些煎饼吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好吃的蓝莓煎饼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克从盆里偷偷往外看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔点了点头，坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他还是很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妻子做饭的时候，食人魔又开始闻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真的闻到了。”食人魔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那个小偷......我知道是他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克皱了皱眉头，食人魔才是真的小偷！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔突然站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他检查了储藏室，又检查了所有的柜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妻子叹了口气：“忘了那个男孩儿吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>来，你的早饭好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>吃完早饭，食人魔拍了拍桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老婆！”他大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把我的金竖琴拿来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“以前爸爸也有一把金竖琴。”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克看着女人把什么东西放在了桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就是那把闪闪发光的金竖琴！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔轻轻摸了摸竖琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我最爱的金竖琴！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“竖琴，唱歌吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金竖琴开始唱歌。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔也闭上眼睛，哼了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多么美妙的音乐啊！”杰克心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以用它赚很多钱！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一定要把竖琴拿回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>